cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques for face photo synthesis. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also utilizes deep learning techniques, which are commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which falls under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
